~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : picture                                   ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : picture [<picturefile>] 

   This command allows you to display an ascii picture to all users in
   the same room as yourself.  An error is displayed if you try to show 
   a picture that does not exist.  Also, typing .picture on its own will 
   list out all available pictures.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : ppicture, preview
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
